Unicron/Teufel:


Unicron blocked Hot Rod's shots with his shield, which was beginning to give 
way pretty good.  He fired a missile down at Hot Rod, followed by a single 
optic blast.

---

Teufel flew hard left,  a few shots digging into his abs doing minor damage.  
He fired off twenty rapid laser blasts from his left shoulder cannon after 
Zardus, and fired a missile from his left launcher attached to his arm at the 
Cybertronian Fire.
